		<div class="content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><br /><strong>中央民族乐团周末音乐会</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> 时间：2012年9月2日              地点：国家大剧院音乐厅       </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">指挥：何建国（国家一级指挥）   首席：唐峰（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">解说：席强（中央民族乐团团长民族音乐理论家）</span></p>
 
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;"><br /><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">一、民族管弦乐《编花篮》                                                    选自“河南民歌组曲”之四   张一兵曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">二、民族管弦乐《思乡曲》                                                                              马思聪曲   李滨扬编曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">三、琵琶与乐队《绽放》                                                              马久越曲   赵聪改编   胡廷江编配</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                                                    琵琶演奏：赵聪<br />                                （国家一级演员、“天华杯”全国专业琵琶大赛金奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">四、声乐与乐队《小河淌水》                                                                          云南民歌   史志有编曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                                             演唱：裴长佳（文华奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">五、民族管弦乐《寻梦上海》                                                                                                       郑冰曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">          </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">六、笛子与乐队《空山望月》                                                                   王时 王次恒曲   姜莹配器</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                                                       笛子演奏：王次恒<br />                                             （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">七、民族管弦乐《阿佤山》                                       选自《滇西土风三首》第一乐章   郭文景曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>		</div>

		
			
